<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:09:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拉宾暗杀喜剧和失控的阴茎吸引年轻的以色列人回到战时剧院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/theater/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rabin-assassination-comedy-and-a-runaway-penis-lure-young-israelis-back-to-wartime-theater/00000190-59c5-d63a-a7b2-5ddf09e00000</link><description>特拉维夫卡梅里剧院的新一代剧团将幽默与震撼人心的内容结合在一起，并不回避政治主题。但加沙战争带来了不同的困境：导演说，外面的世界“太疯狂了，我们开始觉得我们的排练室是世界上唯一正常的地方”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 15:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/theater/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rabin-assassination-comedy-and-a-runaway-penis-lure-young-israelis-back-to-wartime-theater/00000190-59c5-d63a-a7b2-5ddf09e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称人质交易尚未完成，目标是回到谈判桌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-says-hostage-deal-not-close-goal-is-to-get-back-to-negotiating-table/00000190-6942-d9ec-a19e-ef57f8cd0000</link><description>消息人士称，“双方之间的距离”很大，特别是在内塔尼亚胡发表有关“部分协议”的声明之后，而且调解员现在才试图重启谈判。另一位消息人士称，辛瓦尔对达成协议不感兴趣，他更希望北方局势升级而不是结束战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 13:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-says-hostage-deal-not-close-goal-is-to-get-back-to-negotiating-table/00000190-6942-d9ec-a19e-ef57f8cd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察暴力在反政府集会上激增，反对派MK也首当其冲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-violence-spikes-at-anti-govt-rallies-opposition-mk-also-bears-brunt/00000190-68e6-d90c-a7fc-7fe6e5950000</link><description>一名口头攻击抗议者并威胁他的警察将受到调查。据记录，反对派议员纳马·拉齐米在特拉维夫遭到一名警察的暴力推搡。 “内塔尼亚胡政府刑事部长[本-格维尔]的特使掐住我的脖子，揪我的头发，踢我，”她说</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-violence-spikes-at-anti-govt-rallies-opposition-mk-also-bears-brunt/00000190-68e6-d90c-a7fc-7fe6e5950000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯联盟高级官员表示，不再将真主党视为恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/arab-league-no-longer-views-hezbollah-as-terrorist-group-top-official-says/00000190-68ed-d747-add0-e8fd4a5e0000</link><description>阿拉伯联盟助理秘书长霍萨姆·扎基宣布对埃及媒体的政策转变</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 11:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/arab-league-no-longer-views-hezbollah-as-terrorist-group-top-official-says/00000190-68ed-d747-add0-e8fd4a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府批准内塔尼亚胡新办公室和住所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-could-get-two-new-residences-and-an-office-as-govt-set-to-vote-on-building-plan/00000190-6894-d747-add0-e8ddc0db0000</link><description>总理办公室去年宣布，鉴于成本高昂，正在考虑取消贝尔福官方官邸的翻修工程，转而建造新院落。然而最近，该办公室选择耗资数千万谢克尔对其进行翻修，同时也推进新大楼的建设</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 11:39:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-could-get-two-new-residences-and-an-office-as-govt-set-to-vote-on-building-plan/00000190-6894-d747-add0-e8ddc0db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长称，无法逃脱针对真主党的“尖锐、快速”战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/no-escape-from-sharp-quick-war-against-hezbollah-israeli-far-right-minister-says/00000190-687d-d747-add0-e8fd070e0000</link><description>以色列部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇也感谢特朗普在与拜登的总统辩论中拒绝支持巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 10:29:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/no-escape-from-sharp-quick-war-against-hezbollah-israeli-far-right-minister-says/00000190-687d-d747-add0-e8fd070e0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管威胁不断升级，伊朗并不急于与以色列发生直接冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-escalating-threats-iran-isnt-rushing-toward-a-direct-clash-with-israel/00000190-67f1-d499-a5bf-effffb170000</link><description>随着加沙战争的继续，伊朗继续进行心理战，威胁以色列和拜登政府不要对黎巴嫩真主党发动全面军事行动。但它没有宣布将直接参与此类活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 08:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-escalating-threats-iran-isnt-rushing-toward-a-direct-clash-with-israel/00000190-67f1-d499-a5bf-effffb170000</guid></item><item><title>拜登总统辩论惨败可能会诱使美国在中东的敌人考验他的决心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/bidens-presidential-debate-fiasco-may-tempt-u-s-foes-in-the-mideast-to-test-his-resolve/00000190-6594-d0b3-a7d1-67dc5c3e0000</link><description>除了拜登疲倦的表现在民主党中激起前所未有的动荡外，美国的领导力危机预计还将在世界各地引发二次地震，尤其是在中东</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 05:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/bidens-presidential-debate-fiasco-may-tempt-u-s-foes-in-the-mideast-to-test-his-resolve/00000190-6594-d0b3-a7d1-67dc5c3e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府一致再次任命丹尼·达农为以色列下一任驻联合国特使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-expected-to-re-appoint-danny-dannon-as-israels-next-envoy-to-un/00000190-6525-d747-add0-edfd99610000</link><description>利库德集团成员丹尼·达农将接替过去四年担任以色列驻联合国大使的吉拉德·埃尔丹。这将是达农第二次担任该职位，他于 2015 年至 2020 年间担任该职位</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-expected-to-re-appoint-danny-dannon-as-israels-next-envoy-to-un/00000190-6525-d747-add0-edfd99610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称黎巴嫩无人机在戈兰高地爆炸；反坦克导弹击中以色列北部地区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-live/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-freed-hostages-urge-government-to-reach-deal/00000190-66f3-d90c-a7fc-77f73c5b0000</link><description>伊斯兰圣战组织图勒凯姆营的主要特工在以色列袭击中身亡 ■ 梅图拉委员会：真主党导弹对房屋造成破坏 ■ 自 43 年 10 月 7 日以来，过去 24 小时内，加沙有 37,877 名巴勒斯坦人丧生 ■ 以色列国防军：加沙市的学校、诊所被以色列使用恐怖组织 ■ 以色列国防军决定，以色列军队高层现在必须批准杀死加沙 10 月 7 日恐怖分子</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 02:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-live/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-freed-hostages-urge-government-to-reach-deal/00000190-66f3-d90c-a7fc-77f73c5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布两名士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/two-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-combat-israeli-army-announces/00000190-6580-d499-a5bf-edbec73a0000</link><description>这两名士兵被确认为参谋中士。 Yair Avitan，20 岁，中士。一等（res.）Yakir Shmuel Tatelbaum，21；据以色列国防军称，另有两名士兵受重伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 22:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/two-soldiers-killed-in-north-gaza-combat-israeli-army-announces/00000190-6580-d499-a5bf-edbec73a0000</guid></item><item><title>获救人质诺亚·阿加马尼敦促“尽一切可能”释放所有人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/rescued-hostage-noa-argamani-urges-doing-everything-possible-to-release-all-hostages/00000190-657d-d367-abbc-6f7f8a130000</link><description>阿加马尼在六月初从哈马斯囚禁中获救后首次公开讲话中表示，“我们不能忘记仍被哈马斯囚禁的人质，我们必须尽一切可能将他们带回家”</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 21:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/rescued-hostage-noa-argamani-urges-doing-everything-possible-to-release-all-hostages/00000190-657d-d367-abbc-6f7f8a130000</guid></item><item><title>美国向哈马斯提供修改以色列支持的加沙停火提案的机会，希望达成妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-offers-hamas-chance-to-amend-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-backed-by-israel/00000190-6523-d499-a5bf-edbfde3b0000</link><description>消息人士称，加沙停火谈判尚未取得任何突破，而哈马斯宣布其政治领导人已与埃及情报部门负责人会面讨论谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 18:36:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-offers-hamas-chance-to-amend-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-backed-by-israel/00000190-6523-d499-a5bf-edbfde3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 267 天：以色列国防军称真主党无人机在以色列西加利利地区爆炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-267-idf-says-hezbollah-drones-exploded-in-israels-western-galilee/00000190-64ca-d367-abbc-6fca28640000</link><description>以色列国防部长：“我们并不是在寻求战争，但我们已经做好了战争准备” ■ 无人机、导弹在以色列加利利地区引发火灾 ■ 美国提出停火/人质释放协议的“新措辞” ■ 伊朗的联合国使命警告称，如果以色列对黎巴嫩“发动全面军事侵略”，“毁灭性战争将会接踵而至” ■ 战争进入 267 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 17:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-267-idf-says-hezbollah-drones-exploded-in-israels-western-galilee/00000190-64ca-d367-abbc-6fca28640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人集会反对内塔尼亚胡联盟，要求加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/continuing-the-war-means-israel-will-murder-hostages-families-demand-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-6488-d9ec-a19e-e79d4e520000</link><description>一名人质亲属表示，“我们和亲人之间的障碍是内塔尼亚胡坚持不把结束战争作为协议的一部分”。 ■ 警察在特拉维夫抗议活动中强行推搡反对派议员纳马·拉齐米。恳求政府确保加沙所有剩余人质获释</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 15:59:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/continuing-the-war-means-israel-will-murder-hostages-families-demand-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-6488-d9ec-a19e-e79d4e520000</guid></item><item><title>守卫以色列驻塞尔维亚大使馆的警察中箭受伤；袭击者被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-29/ty-article/police-officer-guarding-israeli-embassy-in-serbia-wounded-by-arrow-attacker-shot-dead/00000190-63e4-d9ec-a19e-e7f518130000</link><description>守卫以色列驻贝尔格莱德大使馆的警察颈部被箭射中，随后开枪打死袭击者，目前袭击者身份仍在确定中</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 12:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-29/ty-article/police-officer-guarding-israeli-embassy-in-serbia-wounded-by-arrow-attacker-shot-dead/00000190-63e4-d9ec-a19e-e7f518130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院暂时禁止地方议会没收约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的牛群</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/high-court-temporarily-forbids-local-council-from-sezing-palestinians-herds-in-west-bank/00000190-62e8-d90c-a7fc-77ecb3040000</link><description>近几个月来，约旦河谷地区委员会扣押了属于巴勒斯坦人的牛群或羊群，理由是它们徘徊或阻碍交通。法院命令理事会停止行动，直到有关此事的请愿得到解决</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 08:19:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/high-court-temporarily-forbids-local-council-from-sezing-palestinians-herds-in-west-bank/00000190-62e8-d90c-a7fc-77ecb3040000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派走上以色列街头，因征兵问题与警方发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-take-to-israels-streets-clash-with-police-over-conscription-to-military/00000190-5eb9-d506-ab9a-7efbc1b50000</link><description>正统派抗议者封锁了一条主要高速公路，恳求他们的政治领导人不要在以色列国防军入伍问题上妥协。大多数人都喊着常见的口号，比如“我们会死，不会被征召入伍”，但也有一些人提出了不同的口号。一名男子对警察大喊：“很遗憾他们没有在 10 月 7 日解决掉你”</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 06:15:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-take-to-israels-streets-clash-with-police-over-conscription-to-military/00000190-5eb9-d506-ab9a-7efbc1b50000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在加沙北部丧生；获释人质敦促政府达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article-live/irans-mission-to-un-if-israel-attacks-lebanon-an-obliterating-war-will-ensue/00000190-61e4-d90c-a7fc-77e4c4ba0000</link><description>以色列国防军：两名士兵在加沙北部的战斗中受重伤 ■ 以色列军队称，部队在加沙城的战斗中杀死了“数十名”恐怖分子 ■ 袭击者在打伤守卫以色列驻塞尔维亚大使馆的警察后被击毙 ■ 以色列军队称，向社区发射了三枚反坦克导弹在国家的北部；没有人员伤亡报告 ■ 两枚火箭从以色列南部加沙地带发射；暂无人员伤亡报告</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 03:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article-live/irans-mission-to-un-if-israel-attacks-lebanon-an-obliterating-war-will-ensue/00000190-61e4-d90c-a7fc-77e4c4ba0000</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构报告称，伊朗计划在福尔多安装一半新离心机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/iran-installs-half-of-planned-new-centrifuges-at-fordow-iaea-report-says/00000190-60bf-d499-a5bf-e9bfc5930000</link><description>外交官表示，增加IR-6机器是对国际原子能机构35国理事会6月5日针对伊朗的一项决议的回应，该决议呼吁德黑兰加强与监督机构的合作，并撤销最近禁止检查人员的做法</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 21:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/iran-installs-half-of-planned-new-centrifuges-at-fordow-iaea-report-says/00000190-60bf-d499-a5bf-e9bfc5930000</guid></item></channel></rss>